   mintExtensionNew(['0x....1', '0x....2'], [1, 2], [])
       Mints a single new token, and gives 1 to '0x....1' and 2 to '0x....2'.  Token uses default uri.

   mintExtensionNew(['0x....1'], [1, 2], ["", "http://token2.com"])
